    <item>
      <title>鲁贝尼在特朗普变成“理性”之前看到了更多的市场下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/roubini-sees-more-market-declines-before-trump-turns-rational</link>
      <description><![CDATA[努里尔·鲁贝尼（Nouriel Roubini）预测，随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）拨打他的全球贸易攻击，股市更正可能会加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/roubini-sees-more-market-declines-before-trump-turns-rational</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 11:00:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于强大的工作数据无法平息关税担忧，美国股票跌落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/us-stock-futures-sink-as-china-retaliates-against-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票周五在过去七个星期中的六个星期中跌倒，因为强大的劳动数据并没有减轻对贸易战对国内经济的影响的焦虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/us-stock-futures-sink-as-china-retaliates-against-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:43:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EM资产随着中国的报复而受到打击，LATAM货币带头损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/emerging-currencies-gain-in-asia-as-tariff-woes-weigh-on-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲的货币周五跌倒，智利和墨西哥比索带来的损失和新兴股票跌落，因为在中国宣布卖出泰特（Tit-Tat）措施之后，美国征收美国关税的后果延长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/emerging-currencies-gain-in-asia-as-tariff-woes-weigh-on-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 08:32:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克的技术湿巾的“最坏情况”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/-worst-case-scenario-for-tech-wipes-1-4-trillion-from-nasdaq</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的新关税政权下，这是一个世纪以来最严厉的，几乎没有任何地方可以隐藏许多美国技术公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/-worst-case-scenario-for-tech-wipes-1-4-trillion-from-nasdaq</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 08:14:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税战争掩盖了稳固的工作：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票在世界各地跌落，债券飙升，石油跌至四年低位，中国加强了与唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战的斗争，以加剧对经济的担忧，尽管迹象表现出坚实的就业市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
